### What changed
- Extended "When to Use" with C++/CMake-specific triggers: Containerfile adoption, Makefile variable replacement pattern
- Added Step 7 (C++/CMake Makefile migration): replacing `DOCKER_CHECK`/`DOCKER_PREFIX` with `CONTAINER_CHECK`/`CONTAINER_PREFIX`, removing `ifeq ($(NATIVE),1)` block, removing `%.native` pattern rule, renaming `docker.*` â†’ `container.*` targets
- Added Step 8 (justfile for C++/CMake): removing `NATIVE=1` from make calls, renaming `make docker.up` â†’ `make container.up`
